# .env.example — Environment Variables Template
# ===============================================
# This is a SAFE placeholder file — it contains no real secrets.
# It is safe to push this file to GitHub.
#
# ── HOW TO USE ──
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to .env
#       Windows: copy .env.example .env
#       Mac/Linux: cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Open .env and replace the placeholder with your real Groq API key
#
# 3. Get your free Groq API key at: https://console.groq.com
#
# ⚠️  NEVER push your real .env file to GitHub
#     The .env file is already listed in .gitignore for your safety

# Groq API Key — required for question_generator, answer_evaluator, ats_scorer
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here